

Allow lists of "favorites" (e.g. "Home to work", "Work to home", "Busses from Sullivan")
Allow editing of favorites by showing all busses stopping near a location (picked from map or GPS current location)



Notes:
Accessing MBTA real-time data is documented here:
http://www.eot.state.ma.us/developers/realtime/

--- Cheat sheet --

To get all routes:
wget -O- http://webservices.nextbus.com/service/publicXMLFeed?command=routeList\&a=mbta

To get all stops for a particular route (e.g. route 747):
wget -O- http://webservices.nextbus.com/service/publicXMLFeed?command=routeConfig\&a=mbta\&r=701
